item.title: CVE-2023-44220|2024-09-09T15:18:00.346Z -- sonicwall -- netextender
item.description: SonicWall NetExtender Windows (32-bit and 64-bit) client 10.2.336 and earlier versions have a DLL Search Order Hijacking vulnerability in the start-up DLL component. Successful exploitation via a local attacker could result in command execution in the target system.

item.title: CVE-2024-29014|2024-08-02T01:03:51.738Z -- sonicwall -- netextender
item.description: Vulnerability in SonicWall SMA100 NetExtender Windows (32 and 64-bit) client 10.2.339 and earlier versions allows an attacker to arbitrary code execution when processing an EPC Client update.
